      <title>土耳其 Koc 称 Yapi 信贷销售谈判处于初步阶段</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/turkey-s-koc-says-talks-for-yapi-kredi-sale-at-preliminary-stage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其企业集团 Koc Holding 表示，根据媒体报道，该公司正在就出售其贷款机构 Yapi ve Kredi Bankasi AS 进行初步讨论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/turkey-s-koc-says-talks-for-yapi-kredi-sale-at-preliminary-stage</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 09:18:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
